[h3 id=Ingamecheatcodes
 
	" Ingame cheat codes
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Below the health meter is your points counter. Every time you kill an enemy, you gain 1 point. When you pause and press a key twice, the game converts 10 points into something useful.
	$LF
]p
[table 
	[tbody 
		[tr 
			[th 
				"Button combination pressed
			]th
			[th 
				"Effect
			]th
			[th 
				"Notes
			]th
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Up+Up
			]td
			[td 
				"Laser weapon 
			]td
			[td 
				" 
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Right+Right
			]td
			[td 
				"Autofiring weapon
			]td
			[td 
				" 
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Down+Down
			]td
			[td 
				"Huge bullet weapon 
			]td
			[td 
				"The bullets fired by this weapon will pass through breakable blocks and can kill anything in one hit, even immune enemies/objects
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"Left+Left
			]td
			[td 
				"Bouncing bullet weapon
			]td
			[td 
				" 
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"A+A 
			]td
			[td 
				"Refills jetpack fuel
			]td
			[td 
				"Works in Super Stages only
			]td
		]tr
		[tr 
			[td 
				"B+B 
			]td
			[td 
				"Sets health to 5
			]td
			[td 
				" 
			]td
		]tr
	]tbody
]table
[p 
	"In boss rooms, only the A+A and B+B codes will work.
	$LF
]p
